## Why dbt is the critical layer

dbt sits at the center of the modern data stack as the 
**structured context layer** — it connects raw data with 
AI systems by providing:

- **Rich context & metadata** — AI models understand what the data means
- **Centrally defined semantics** — one source of truth for all teams
- **dbt MCP Server** — direct integration with LLMs like Claude

## Key insight for AI + dbt

Without dbt, AI systems hallucinate because they don't 
understand the data structure. With dbt, you give LLMs 
the context they need to reason correctly about your data.

## Key takeaway

dbt guarantees data quality BEFORE building dashboards.
This is what separates reliable analysis from guesswork.

